rComments: Professor Derek is easily the best prof I have ever had. His lectures are amazing and his powerpoint slides are very detailed. His tests and assignments are graded fairly and he is always willing to discuss them. He is also very approachable during office hours and replies to emails within hours. It shows that he cares about his students.
Very informative and intelligent guy. Completely willing to assist the student in a variety of ways. Did I mention he's also really cute?

Great new prof. First year teaching but has very helpful material on the course websites (and great powerpoints!). Overall, very interesting. Although he's so cute I can't concentrate on the lecture sometimes.
